{"tid":1159790,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭江門接受醫療人工智能領域成果推介","createTime":"2019-05-18T03:38:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-18T05:52:23.000Z","uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"972e8a60e59685de8b90092c6313f1ec52c8e3ee","tid":1159790,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T03:38:28.000Z","msg":"行政長官林鄭月娥下午轉抵江門市，繼續大灣區訪問，她與隨行的政制及內地事務局長聶德權到當地的科技園和博物館參觀。<br />\n<br />\n參觀「珠西創谷科技園」期間，多個落戶江門的港資中小企向林鄭月娥介紹科研成果，包括環保、教育、醫療人工智能等領域。<br />\n<br />\n這個科技園主要是吸引粵港澳台及海外高科技企業進駐， 園區有約50間港澳台企業，有超過100名港澳台人員工作。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1458067-20190517.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1458067-20190517.htm&d=LRk9npnliL4HefRMP%2BWOkCEyVFbloTKGHdwbQdNTMZo%3D&h=c25d085c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1458067-20190517.htm&h=ee07d369\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1458067-20190517.htm</a>"},{"pid":"8b0cf0c681fd53afcb8a750a925aa21850d0b0b7","tid":1159790,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T03:58:27.000Z","msg":"換腦? <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14c8b43e1fc6afff9c2e6476f39dd7be5fe9f437","tid":1159790,"uid":35814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8b0cf0c681fd53afcb8a750a925aa21850d0b0b7","tid":1159790,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T03:58:27.000Z","msg":"換腦? <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T04:00:59.000Z","msg":"植入晶片<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5293f83bbec1c5ad5359c6d997fdcb20543cd26","tid":1159790,"uid":149494,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T04:05:16.000Z","msg":"當港豬們仲係香港上openrice搵餐廳打卡post IG同夜晚追住tvb睇倚天既時候<b